Run source-code adversaries against a local repository

Usage:
  adversary [flags]
  adversary [command]

Available Commands:
  completion  Generate shell completion code
  help        Help about any command
  init        Create a new adversary project
  inspect     Inspect a locally stored adversary or local runtime configuration
  list        List locally stored adversaries
  login       Authenticate with Adversary Labs
  logout      Log out of Adversary Labs
  pack        Package the current adversary into the local content-addressable store
  pull        Pull and install an adversary from an OCI registry
  push        Push a locally packed adversary to an OCI registry
  run         Run an Adversary against a local source repository
  search      Search Adversary Labs adversaries
  store       Inspect and maintain the artifact repository
  validate    Validate an adversary project with the canonical v1 manifest parser
  version     Print the adversary version
  whoami      Show the current Adversary Labs login

Flags:
      --api-url string   Adversary Labs API endpoint (or ADVERSARY_API_URL) (default "https://adversarylabs.ai/api")
  -h, --help             help for adversary
      --profile string   credential profile (default "default")
  -v, --version          version for adversary

Use "adversary [command] --help" for more information about a command.
